                                <title>Gǝʿǝz-Amharic vocabulary</title>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                                <locus from="20" to="33"/>
                                <title>Arabic-Gǝʿǝz vocabulary</title>
                                <note>Arabic words are written in Ethiopic script, e.g., 
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">አላህ፡ ብሂል፡ እግዚአብሔር። ንጅም፡ ብ፡ ኮከብ። ንጁማት፡ ብ፡ ከዋክብት። አሸምሽ፡ ብ፡ ፀሐይ። እልቀመር፡ ብ፡ ወርኅ። አክትብ፡ ጸሐፍ። ከተብኩ፡ ጸሐፍኩ፡</q>. 
                                    It also contains the Arabic numbers and Lord's Prayer.
                                </note>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
